  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3148433/" class="title-link">狼群 狼性</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3148433"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/38625672/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/38625672/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我心狂野</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-04-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-04-08 21:43:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3148433_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  狼群，读了两遍，第二遍最近才读完，每次读都热些沸腾，狼群中的男人把男人体现的淋漓尽致，都是让人热些沸腾的男人，比起现在流行的那些男不男女不女的所谓潮男，让我觉得得痛快，这样的男人才是男人。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
